data.description: For your consideration- comfortable 1 story on a quiet street. Your new home lives in an award-winning community of Canyon Lakes West, “The Manor”, gated and guarded. Conveniently located close to I-99 and 290, in CY-Fair school district.  This 3 BDR/2 Bath/2 car garage, has a formal dining room and a very comfortable floor plan. Eye pleasing brick exterior with a cozy front porch and generous yard with sprinkler system. Your primary bedroom  has high ceilings, large bathroom with dual sinks, and separate tub and shower. Your kitchen has an island, granite countertops, plenty of cabinets, stainless appliances, and is open to the very large family room. Additional room can be used as a game room, and office, playroom for the kids (it’s nestled between two secondary bedrooms), or anything your heart desires. The neighborhood has pool, clubhouse, gym, lake with a walking trail and shared amenities between Marvida, Miramesa and Stone Gate.  You will love it here!
